Installing to the system store is not yet supported on this Linux 😣 but Firefox and/or Chrome/Chromium will still work.
You can also manually install the root certificate at "/home/jz/.local/share/mkcert/rootCA.pem".
The local CA is now installed in the Firefox and/or Chrome/Chromium trust store \(requires browser restart\)! 🦊

For CLI usage run
source <\(locals env\)
